Type: Package
Package: template.dashboard
Title: Boilerplate for 'tidylab' Dashboards
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2022-06-23
Authors@R: 
    person("Harel", "Lustiger", , "tidylab@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Harel Lustiger <tidylab@gmail.com>
Description: Preconfigured dashboard that supports continuous development
    and deployment of a Shiny application. Committing to master branch
    triggers: * Dashboard deployment to https://www.shinyapps.io/ (via
    `rsconnect`); and * Package website deployment (via `pkgdown`).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://tidylab.github.io/template.dashboard/
BugReports: https://github.com/tidylab/template.dashboard/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
Imports: 
    bs4Dash (>= 2.0.0),
    config (>= 0.3.1),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0),
    golem (>= 0.3.2),
    purrr,
    shiny (>= 1.7.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-GB
